I"É<p>The weather forecast is a card to display the weather. Very useful to include on interfaces that people display on the wall.</p>
<p class='img'>
<img src='/images/lovelace/lovelace_weather.png' alt='Screenshot of the weather card'>
Screenshot of the weather card.
</p>
<div class="config-vars">
  <h3><a class="title-link" name="configuration-variables" href="#configuration-variables"></a> Configuration Variables</h3>
  <dl class=''><dt><a class='title-link' name='type' href='#type'></a> type</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>weather-forecast</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='entity' href='#entity'></a> entity</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>The <code>entity_id</code> of the <code>weather</code> platform to use.</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='name' href='#name'></a> name</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Overwrites the friendly name.</p>
</span></p><p class='default'>
Default value: <p>Entity Name</p>
</p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='theme' href='#theme'></a> theme</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Set to any theme within <code>themes.yaml</code></p>
</span></p></dd></dl>
</div>
<p>Example</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml">type: weather-forecast
entity: weather.dark_sky
</code></pre>
<div class="note">
<p>This card works only with platforms that define a <code>weather</code> entity.</p>
<p>E.g., it works with <a href="/integrations/weather.darksky/">Dark Sky</a> but not <a href="/integrations/darksky">Dark Sky Sensor</a></p>
</div>
:ET